Class AbstractBugTrackerPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fortify.pub.bugtracker.plugin.AbstractBugTrackerPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BugTrackerPlugin
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractBatchBugTrackerPlugin

    public abstract class AbstractBugTrackerPlugin
extends java.lang.Object
implements BugTrackerPlugin
    This is the abstract class from which all plugins implementing BugTrackerPlugin would extend. Usage of this abstract class is highly recommended so that backward compatibility support can be utilized whenever available.
